  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will showcase how to create a Trade-in ticket, including:</p><ul><li><p>Attaching a customer</p></li><li><p>Adding trade-in items</p></li><li><p>Selling something to offset trade credit</p></li><li><p>Processing payments</p></li><li><p>Creating Refurb tickets</p></li><li><p>Editing Refurb tickets: attaching parts and labor, moving items to in stock</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/nbIZ-W57bRI\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/nbIZ-W57bRI</a><h2 id=\"CreatingaTrade-InTicket(video)-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933246606/Trade-in+Ticket+Workflow\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933246606\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Trade-in Ticket Workflow</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932656763/Catalog+Items+Creating+Sellable+Repairable+and+Trade-in+Devices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932656763\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Catalog Items: Creating Sellable, Repairable, and Trade-in Devices</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933639827/Assign+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+to+Accept+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933639827\" data-linked-resource-version=\"22\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Starting a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) to Accept Payments</a> </p><p> </p>",
